title: Switch (feat. Reagan Gomez)
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
This week we’re joined by actor/producer, Reagan Gomez, to discuss her new web series, women of color creating their own content and Waka Flocka’s weed.

Check out Reagan’s original series, Almost Home here: http://bit.ly/1ssKQyt

Make sure you support the upcoming series, Surviving The Dead, by donating here:  https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/surviving-the-dead
